title: [Boreas Ridge, Zephyr Lane]
description: Boxwood bushes set with small lanterns line both sides of the meticulously kept path here, trimmed into neat rigid rectangles that outline the sinuous way.  Darkness presses in through thick foliage, the sounds of the forest filling the air.
